Class ServletApiRequest

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.jetty.ee10.servlet.ServletApiRequest
All Implemented Interfaces:
jakarta.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest, jakarta.servlet.ServletRequest
Direct Known Subclasses:
ServletApiRequest.CrossContextForwarded, ServletApiRequest.CrossContextIncluded
public class ServletApiRequest extends Object implements jakarta.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest
The Jetty implementation of the ee10 HttpServletRequest object. This provides the bridge from Servlet HttpServletRequest to the Jetty Core Request via the ServletContextRequest.
